{"tid":1682400,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【共建「黃色經濟圈」】齊振興真香港經濟 讓良心無後顧之憂","createTime":"2019-10-30T04:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T12:35:56.000Z","uid":185631,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"981b9ccfc67d95b97831883dfa142e70f2264ab8","tid":1682400,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:33:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CR9QEMJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCR9QEMJ.jpg&h=de131c28&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n <br />\n只要我哋努力幫襯良心黃店，將真香港人嘅資金同經濟活動，集中返喺我哋真香港人身上，最終就可以創造出自給自足嘅「黃色經濟圈」！<br />\n <br />\n到時我哋會：<br />\n <br />\n一. 齊齊賺錢<br />\n大家集中幫襯黃店，刺激黃色經濟圈，資金就會喺返圈子裡面流動同增值，黃店越賺得多，越去返其他黃店消費，其他黃店老闆同員工都受惠，周而復始，越做越強大。<br />\n <br />\n二. 安心消費<br />\n以後只幫襯黃店，就唔使怕益咗一班冇良心、冇道德嘅藍店，一邊減少佢哋收入，一邊消費得心安理得，心情都好啲。<br />\n <br />\n三. 無後顧之憂<br />\n而家香港好多人唔敢表態，好大程度係因為驚無生意、無咗份工。只要黃色經濟圈成形，擁有一定嘅經濟基礎可以自給自足，咁就唔使怕因為發聲而失去藍色、紅色嘅收入來源，大家都可以最返個講香港人話嘅真香港人。<br />\n <br />\n四. 利用「少數霸權法則」擴展經濟圈<br />\n經濟法則嘅一種，可以迫到中立同藍店都改變立場，加入「黃金經濟圈」。詳情請睇下文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1679102/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1679102/page/1</a><br />\n <br />\n五. 明白到世界唔係得人民幣<br />\n電影《小丑JOKER》冇喺中國上映，一樣成為歷史上最賣座嘅R級片，淨賺36億2000萬港元。無中國票房都可以成為世界第一，呢個例子可以令我哋記返起&mdash;&mdash;世界唔係得人民幣市場，唔係冇咗佢就等於世界末日（何況近年中國經濟泡沫開始爆破，又俾全世界圍堵）。只要香港人努力做好本份，一樣可以賺到錢、發到達。唔好忘記，中國經濟有咁嘅成就，全靠全球第八大富有嘅香港幾十年嚟畀錢佢哋發展，經濟發展一向係我哋香港人最強項。<br />\n  <br />\n建立黃色經濟圈，對香港人真係百利而無一害，只要我哋努力用意志、用良心消費，自然會得到對得住良心嘅成效。希望大家可以的起心肝，一齊用最安全、香港人最強項嘅方法救港啦！<br />\n<br />\nCopy from: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2417735138469124\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D2417735138469124&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt34ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=62bf37d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2417735138469124</a>"},{"pid":"b8e4a51511fa882201f7b909ea0f47d50dfc54ec","tid":1682400,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:34:03.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc5833931933caf530a45516569bc9ade6a0acc","tid":1682400,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:34:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">已經有13個英美參議員/單位就GPhone出聲<br />\n快啲Rt and like and reply哂佢<br />\n全部響哂 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">/Task1</span></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt34ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=cb16a2ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>"},{"pid":"195e042670c31589ca042a2f5567172b6b6b7b38","tid":1682400,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:41:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"69d3b7ad23225d0c99fd33630816ea504d71d3c7","tid":1682400,"uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:47:00.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n順便問下左下國嗰隻乜黎"},{"pid":"c0deb6e08834e7dc9b1cfb8495d8d15b95d1c03e","tid":1682400,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T05:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c595f006877da72ecb9779ba3ff52a74a5b006d8","tid":1682400,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69d3b7ad23225d0c99fd33630816ea504d71d3c7","tid":1682400,"uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"